com.yworks.yfiles.view

Class ModelManager<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.view.ModelManager<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of items this instance deals with.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FocusIndicatorManager, HighlightIndicatorManager, SelectionIndicatorManager

    public abstract class ModelManager<T>
extends Object
    Manages the visual representations of items in a CanvasControl.

      • getCanvasObjectGroup

        protected abstract ICanvasObjectGroup getCanvasObjectGroup(T item)
        Callback used by install(java.lang.Object) to retrieve the canvas object group for a given item.

        Returning null will cause install(java.lang.Object) not to install anything.

        Parameters:

        Returns:
        An ICanvasObjectGroup or null

      • getInstaller

        protected abstract ICanvasObjectInstaller getInstaller(T item)
        Callback used by install(java.lang.Object) to retrieve the installer for a given item.

        Implementations may use the ILookup.lookup(java.lang.Class) of the item.

        Returning null will cause install(java.lang.Object) not to install anything.

        Parameters:
        item - The item to find an installer for.
        Returns:
        An installer or null

      • install

        protected ICanvasObject install(T item)
        Installs a member of the collection into the canvas using the ICanvasObjectDescriptor which is returned by getInstaller(java.lang.Object).
        Parameters:
        item - The member to install.
        Returns:
        The canvas object that has been returned by the installer.

      • isEnabled

        public final boolean isEnabled()
        Gets whether this ModelManager is enabled.

        If the manager is disabled, it will not install the ICanvasObjects into the associated CanvasControl.

        The default is true, i.e. this manager is enabled by default.

        Returns:
        true if enabled; false otherwise.
        See Also:
        setEnabled(boolean)
